Version 1.3.3, 12 October 2017
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Feature - New wildcard for postcode matching @ which matches multiple characters
* Fix - Multiple currencies not supported in subtotal condition
* Fix - Incorrect logic in postcode condition check
* Fix - Postcode matching is case sensitive
* Tweak - Other minor bug fixes and improvements

Version 1.3.2, 14 April 2017
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Tweak - Improved compatibility with WooCommerce 3.0
* Tweak - Other minor bug fixes and improvements

Version 1.3.1, 17 June 2016
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Fix - Error related to use of function return value in write context

Version 1.3, 17 June 2016
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Feature - Additional charges per product category
* Feature - Option to automatically select the most expensive shipping method
* Feature - New numeric operators in conditions - not more than, more than
* Fix - Compatibility issue with Subscriptio extension
* Tweak - Support for WooCommerce Shipping Zones
* Tweak - Improved compatibility with WooCommerce 2.6
* Tweak - Improved compatibility with other plugins that use Select2
* Tweak - Deprecated proprietary shipping zones in favour of new WC shipping zones

Version 1.2.1, 12 April 2016
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Tweak - Improved compatibility with Wordpress 4.5
* Tweak - Other minor bug fixes and improvements

Version 1.2, 6 February 2016
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Feature - Weight unit multiplier (e.g. allows to set cost per 0.5 kg/lbs)
* Feature - Option to round weight up to full weight unit
* Feature - New condition method "only selected"
* Feature - Option to enter shipping rates and additional charges inclusive of tax
* Feature - Duplicate shipping methods, charges and zones
* Fix - Issue with some conditions when "all of selected" method is used
* Tweak - Improved shipping rate refresh method, now takes option changes into account
* Tweak - Improved language file loading - now also looks in WP_LANG_DIR
* Tweak - Other minor bug fixes and improvements

Version 1.1, 11 December 2015
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Feature - Additional Charge subjects - cart, cart line item and quantity unit
* Feature - Added support for automatic updates
* Fix - Last order time condition bug
* Fix - Conditions method "All of selected" bug
* Tweak - Added supported WordPress and WooCommerce version checks
* Tweak - Other minor bug fixes and improvements

Version 1.0, 1 November 2015
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Initial release
